They should make this a boot enchantment and then buff the existing boot enchantments to keep up. I would even consider putting this enchantment on the green (Alacrity) boot enchant.

{{item:1331}} 

UNIQUE - Alacrity: +25 Movement Speed.
UNIQUE - Shadow Walk: Ignore unit collision.

{{item:1332}} 

UNIQUE - Captain: Grants +20% Movement Speed to approaching allied champions. (Maybe increase the aura to 1500 from 1100).

{{item:1333}} 

UNIQUE - Distortion: Teleport, Flash, and Ghost have 25% reduced cooldown and grant you a {{summoner:4}} 30%, {{summoner:12}} 40%, {{summoner:6}} 20% speed boost for {{summoner:4}} 2.5 seconds, {{summoner:12}} 5 seconds, {{summoner:6}} the duration of the normal Ghost speed increase.

{{item:1330}} 

UNIQUE - Furor:  Grants 20% bonus movement speed that decays over 2.5 seconds whenever you deal damage with a single target ability (excluding damage over time) or basic attack (on-hit).

then, just change Phantom Dancer to have the same unique passive:

UNIQUE â€“ SPECTRAL WALTZ: Grants +12% movement speed and UNIQUE: Shadow Walk while within 500 units of a visible enemy champion.

With how much they are re-working champions and items I think changing boot enchantments to have a more noticeable effect yet help reinforce your champion's mobility pattern in game would be a step in the right direction.
